Brickcoder is for Programming your Lego (c) Mindstorms (c) NXT using NXC (not eXactly C). It is based on C with Gtk+ (GIMP Toolkit). 

Log:

 * 0.4.2 - Improved Compiling, more objective using headerfiles, better menus (added icons).

 * 0.4.1 - First release on github

Planned features:

 * Code Highlighting
 
 * using GtkSourceView

 * Projects

 * NXT-Sound Creator

 * Tabbed Editor

I'm working on packages for DEB and RPM. For now you have to compile using ./configure, make and make install. Check-install is possible.
